                            oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                            oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                            oc:textContent "This skill enables conversion from PDF to editable Word documents using **pdf2docx** - a Python library that preserves layout, tables, images, and text formatting. Unlike OCR-based solutions, pdf2docx extracts native PDF content for accurate conversion." ] ;
                    oc:sectionLevel 2 ;
                    oc:sectionOrder 1 ;
                    oc:sectionTitle "Overview" ],
                [ a oc:Section ;
